{"id":1132526766,"question_id":3031,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"5 months, 4 weeks","timestamp":1703975076,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"45 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1132526766/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Construct Product Matrix","memory":"73.2 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    long MOD = 12345;\n    public int[][] constructProductMatrix(int[][] grid) {\n        int n = grid.length;\n        int m = grid[0].length;\n        int[][] res = new int[n][m];\n        long pre = 1, suf = 1;\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n            if (i <= n - i - 1) {\n                Arrays.fill(res[i], 1);\n                Arrays.fill(res[n - i - 1], 1);\n            }\n            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {\n                res[i][j] = (int)(pre * res[i][j] % MOD);\n                res[n - i - 1][m - j - 1] = (int)(suf * res[n - i - 1][m - j - 1] % MOD);\n                pre = pre * grid[i][j] % MOD;\n                suf = suf * grid[n - i - 1][m - j - 1] % MOD;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return res;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"construct-product-matrix","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
